Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Dang...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:28.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo, your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Warm her back by the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! Itachi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's how you hid it, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Get back here, Itachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Papa's precious money...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiromaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro... maru...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.07,0:01:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Saburomaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,How it must've hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How it must've pained you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Those bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiromaru, eat them all up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.39,0:00:18.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめろぉーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:23.02,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こいつはぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.10,0:00:25.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くそっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.69,0:00:28.61,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ。おめぇ背中が
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:33.24,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,背中を火に当てろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:34.99,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やめろ！イタチ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:39.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,見るな！見るな見るなぁー！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.74,0:00:42.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こういう仕掛けだったのか…どろろ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:47.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,行くぞ！てめぇら！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.67,0:00:51.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くっそぉ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.59,0:00:54.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,戻ってこいイタチー！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:00:58.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それはお父ちゃんの大事なお金なんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.68,0:01:03.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.19,0:01:10.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,二郎…丸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:15.57,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,二郎…丸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.07,0:01:19.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,三郎丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:25.54,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,痛かったろう…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.91,0:01:27.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,苦しかったろう…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.67,0:01:34.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいつら…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.18,0:01:40.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,皆殺しにしてやるぅっ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.64,0:01:44.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,二郎丸ー！やつらを食い殺せーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.39,0:02:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Betrayed this world
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And it simmers within
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.81,0:02:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Rupturing my innards
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Swelling a reddish black
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the sun burnt skin ruptures
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.87,0:02:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light  \N in the depths of the seething darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.63,0:02:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices  \N in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.01,0:03:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.97,0:03:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a light  \N in the depths of the darkness
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Confirming each other's voices  \N in the distance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As if to stroke with wet fingertips
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to touch you one day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.01,0:03:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,#18 The story of the cape of no mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure we can trust that map, Boss?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't need for anything  \N as long as I had you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You feared nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You were tied to nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Strong and beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Compared to you, how petty humans are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiromaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are flawless in every way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are nothing but food \Nbefore your greatness!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach them a lesson!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiromaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro... How...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That shark...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,A demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That broken excuse for a human \Nis no match for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Rip those ugly humans apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiromaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, bro... Stop it, what the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I came for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you took long enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I had to go through \Na ton of stuff by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He had your leg, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What a load of crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You went through all this... \NYou killed Jiromaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,just to get a human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,For what, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it that important to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, we can't just stand around. \NItachi is up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place. No doubt about that. \NBut this...?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, we can get in through here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna be rich now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gonna have us the time of our lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-What's that? \N-There's something down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,-Probably the treasure. \N-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the deal, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew you weren't \Nsome good-for-nothing, Hibukuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,B-Boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ain't got guts, go on home.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:42.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Get the treasure or die trying. \NIt's one or the other, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro, is that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,We found a boat, \Nprobably the one Hyakkimaru used.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,There are signs of others \Nsneaking onto this cape too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it's a band of brigands.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill every human being who is a threat \Nto the peace of our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,March!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,They're Daigo's samurai.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the heck are they here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not here \Nto take my treasure, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, the treasure isn't just yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Arrows!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Orders are to not leave \Na single rat alive. Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The loot was almost in my grasp...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,They're all over the beach. \NWe need to find a place to hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiromaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Saburomaru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be together, forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me a few minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:47.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'll head over \Nwith a load of gifts for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Not over there. \N-Must be this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-Itachi. \N-Hey, Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a lot of luck \Nin that tiny frame.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Your papa's treasure \Nis still up in that mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,There were traps everywhere. \NOne wrong step, and boom, you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I could've disarmed them \Nif I had the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't the time for that! \NForget the loot, we have to run.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What if the samurai find it first?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't have them using my money \Nfor some stupid wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Us, too. Boom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually Dororo, it might just work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be hidden around here. \NScour the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They have explosives...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Call the other troop back, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta get to the beach \Nbefore they realize it's a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The demon harming our land of Daigo. \NHyakkimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:13:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Tahomaru...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All that side with the demon \Nwill die here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's our chance, let's run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll all die if we stay, we gotta run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not like before. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master is heir to the land of Daigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Its people, its prosperity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He bears it all on his shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,His resolve far exceeds yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Why kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Your existence alone
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,causes calamities to befall our land.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the enemy of the people of Daigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Release!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit, we gotta hide somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, this place was on your map.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This might be another trap, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the fifth stone from the left is a clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi, give it up already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We could go and live in a better place. \NAll we need is this treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I will shoot you down. \NYou and all that side with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What am I supposed to do now, bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Master, finish him!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Enemies...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You are my enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I will break that left arm of yours, too, \NHyakkimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi, hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo, one last favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me see the treasure, \Njust one glimpse...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You're all going to where \NJiromaru and Saburomaru went.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Dororo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,-Young Master! \N-Mutsu, Hyogo, retreat!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dororo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:22.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyogo... Hyogo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi, Itachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Money...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is... It's really there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,My money...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When you meet Papa up there, \Ndon't quarrel with him this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What you have on your back  \N can move people and change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a source of great power.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how I should use this stuff, \Nso I don't want it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa, Mama. \NWait a bit more 'till I figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,This is different, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little something to keep us going.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hold up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.85,0:03:57.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おかしら…ホントにその地図合ってるんスかぁ？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:04.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あれだ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.37,0:04:16.04,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前たちさえいれば、他には何もいらない。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.59,0:04:20.21,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前たちは何も恐れない
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:22.72,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何にも縛られない。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.51,0:04:25.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,。強くて美しい
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:31.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,それに比べて本当につまらない。人間なんて
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:34.39,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おっかちゃん…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.45,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,二郎丸ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.39,0:05:12.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱり…完璧だぜ。お前たちはさぁ…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:20.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前たちの前じゃ、人間なんざただのエサだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:21.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,思い知らせてやれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.05,0:05:48.30,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.59,0:05:50.80,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:56.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,二郎丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.35,0:05:59.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あに…き、どうして
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:12.08,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あのサメ…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.08,0:06:14.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:18.00,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あんな壊れかけ、お前の敵じゃねぇや。
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.08,0:06:24.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醜い人間なんざ、ぶっ殺してやれぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.22,0:06:33.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.99,0:06:51.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,二郎丸ーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:11.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきー！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.23,0:07:24.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:40.71,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちょ…あにきってば！なんだよいきなり
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.33,0:07:44.17,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,迎えに来た
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.80,0:07:53.76,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ならもっと早く来てくれよ。
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.22,0:07:58.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいら1人で…すっごく大変なだったんだからな！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.15,0:08:04.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:13.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あいつ…足を持ってたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.54,0:08:28.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ハハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.92,0:08:33.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そんなにしてまで…二郎丸まで殺して…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:36.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,わざわざ人間の体なんか…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:38.35,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,何になるってんだよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.81,0:08:41.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でも…取り戻したろう…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.31,0:08:46.06,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…こうしちゃいられないんだ。イタチたちが！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.53,0:08:54.74,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,場所はこの辺で違いなさそうだな。こいつは…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:57.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おかしら！こっから中に入れそうですぜぇ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.37,0:09:01.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これで俺らも長者だぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.66,0:09:04.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,へへっ！都で派手に遊ぶってのもいいよなぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい！ちょっと待て！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:08.13,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだこりゃ！\N奥に何かあるぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.29,0:09:10.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お宝に違ぇねぇ！\Nよっしゃあ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.93,0:09:22.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そういうことかよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:31.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やっぱただのズタ袋じゃなかったなぁアンタ…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おかしら…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.57,0:09:37.82,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,意気地のねぇ奴はとっとと帰れ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.99,0:09:42.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,宝を手に入れるか、罠にかかっておっ死ぬか、2つに1つだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.33,0:09:46.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ん？なんだぁありゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき、あれって…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.27,0:10:14.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,百鬼丸の乗ってきたと思しき船を見つけました。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.98,0:10:18.03,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,他にも多数、入り込んでいる者がいるようです。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おそらく野党の類かと
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.70,0:10:21.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,構わん。
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:26.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,民の安寧を脅かす者ども、1人たりとも生きて帰すな！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.29,0:10:28.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,全軍進め！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:38.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ありゃ醍醐の侍か…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:41.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なんだってこんなとこまで…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:45.22,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,まさかあいつら、俺のお宝を横取りする気じゃねぇよな
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:47.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おい、いつからテメェ1人のモンになったんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.02,0:10:49.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,矢が！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.31,0:10:53.86,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,1匹たりとも逃がすなとのご命令だ！撃てぇー！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:56.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうなってんスかおかしらぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.99,0:10:59.95,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,チッ…お宝は目の前だってのに！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.36,0:11:05.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,浜辺は侍でいっぱいだ。いっぺんどっかに隠れてやり過ごそう！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.54,0:11:07.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いたぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.35,0:11:30.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,二郎丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:32.77,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,三郎丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:36.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺たちはどこまでだって一緒だ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:40.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,もうちっとだけ待っててくれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:47.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,たんまり土産、持ってくからよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:50.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こっちはいない！\Nじゃあこっちだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.30,0:12:04.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっ…イタチ！\Nどろろか…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.51,0:12:08.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おめぇもしぶとさだけは一丁前だなぁ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:12.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,安心しな。お父ちゃんのお宝はまだあの山ん中だぜ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.39,0:12:18.48,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっちこっち罠が仕掛けてあってなぁ。\Nヘタにいじるとたちまちドカンだ。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.86,0:12:21.40,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,時がありゃ取り除いてやれるんだが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:25.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,言ってる場合かよ！宝なんてどうでもいいから逃げねぇと！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:28.16,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,侍どもに見つけられたら終わりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.33,0:12:31.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺のカネを、くだらねぇ戦なんざに使われてたまるか！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.46,0:12:35.63,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ドカン。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:40.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こっちも、ドカン
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.97,0:12:44.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…何言ってんの？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.34,0:12:48.43,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,いや…上手くいくかもしれねぇぜ、どろろ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:57.15,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,この辺りに隠れているはずだ。徹底的に探せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.98,0:13:00.23,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,助け…て…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.61,0:13:04.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,奴…火薬を…持って…いて…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:12.50,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,チッ…別働隊の連中も呼び戻せ！急ぐぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.76,0:13:27.26,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,囮とバレたら、すぐに戻ってくる。今のうちに浜へ出るぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.24,0:13:55.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,我が醍醐の国に仇なす鬼神\N百鬼丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:13:59.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにき…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.21,0:14:02.55,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,多…宝…丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.05,0:14:08.34,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,鬼神に与する者ともども、ここで成敗する！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.19,0:14:19.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきー！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.45,0:14:34.12,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,今のうちだ！ずらかるぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.45,0:14:35.41,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,けど、あにきが！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.58,0:14:38.96,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,このままじゃどのみち全滅だ！一旦退け！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.17,0:14:41.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あにきぃっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:44.42,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:58.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,違う…この前とは…なぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.48,0:15:04.98,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若は醍醐の国の後継。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.15,0:15:07.32,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,民の命と、国の行く末。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:09.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,そのすべてを背負っておられる。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:12.28,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,覚悟が違うのだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.87,0:15:15.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,なぜ俺を…殺す？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.62,0:15:18.29,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様が生きているだけで、
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:21.46,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,醍醐の国は厄災に見舞われ続ける。
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.63,0:15:25.09,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,貴様は、我ら醍醐の敵だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:42.90,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,撃てぇーっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.36,0:15:49.19,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちくしょう…どっか隠れられる場所！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.53,0:15:57.49,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここは…おめぇの地図にあった
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:02.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,こいつも…罠かもしれねぇが…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.75,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,弓手から5番目に、何か手がかりが…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.13,0:16:08.25,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イタチ！もう諦めなよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.55,0:16:14.89,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これがあれは…俺たちはもっとましなところに行けるんだ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.93,0:16:17.81,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イタチ！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.07,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ここで終わらせる！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.08,0:16:42.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,討ち果たす！貴様も、貴様に与する者もすべて！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.80,0:16:56.14,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どうすりゃいいんだよあにきー！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.20,0:17:18.62,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若！とどめを！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.78,0:17:19.78,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,敵…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.67,0:17:29.88,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,敵…お前たちは…俺の…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.34,0:17:32.51,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,やらせない…！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.51,0:17:39.18,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,その左腕の刀も、へし折ってやる。百鬼丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.48,0:17:49.65,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イタチ、しっかり！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.40,0:17:53.94,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ど…どろろ…頼む…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:58.70,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺に一度だけ…カネを拝ませて…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:00.53,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,くれ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.13,0:18:21.97,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前たち…みんな…二郎丸と三郎丸のところへ行け…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.56,0:18:24.68,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,はっ！どろろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:45.37,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,若！\N陸奥、兵庫！退け！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:05.47,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,どろろ…！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.03,0:19:22.91,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.66,0:19:28.33,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,兵庫…兵庫！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.43,0:19:48.31,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,イタチ、イタチ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.48,0:19:53.60,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,カネ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.53,0:20:07.20,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あった…あったぜ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:10.58,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,俺の…カ…ネ…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.84,0:21:04.01,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あっちでお父ちゃんと会っても、今度はケンカしないでおくれよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:17.56,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お前さんの背中のそれは、人を動かし世を変える、
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.73,0:21:20.73,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,でかい力の源になる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.40,0:21:28.66,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,おいらには、こいつの使い方がわかんないからさ…今はまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.71,0:21:38.83,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,お父ちゃん…おっかちゃん。もうちょっとだけ待ってておくんな
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.72,0:21:46.84,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,ちょ…ちょっと待って。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.72,0:21:52.93,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,これはその…別勘定だから。
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:55.85,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,当然の軍資金ってやつだから。な？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.44,0:21:59.36,Default - Copy,,0,0,0,,あ…待ってよあにき！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.91,0:22:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Born into this world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.53,0:22:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no salvation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.08,0:22:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The distorted shape of the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet it beats courageously
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.00,0:23:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no turning back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Even from the path of evil
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.05,0:23:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing the withering seasons
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.51,0:23:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,We search for the truth
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.60,0:23:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,In our ugliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.43,0:23:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't even recognize the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.06,0:23:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As we peel back the skin
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.98,0:23:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We are forever tormented by our stupidity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.62,0:23:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,But if the dawn never comes
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.12,0:23:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Through the painful night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.25,0:23:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You who distrusts nothing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.37,0:23:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You will be able to love  \N this accursed world
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.42,0:23:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we carry the world  \N on our shoulders
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.84,0:23:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to take it back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.01,0:23:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,"Jiromaru"
